=== INTRODUCTION ===

This is a simple status bar widget written (mostly) in Ruby and Cocoa with MacRuby to help keep track of time.
It integrates with Google Calendar using the GCal4Ruby gem.

Once it's running, click the icon on the status bar to open the widget. Click the status bar icon
again to close it.

=== INSTALLATION ===

1) Install GCal4Ruby gem locally

http://cookingandcoding.com/gcal4ruby

% cd <path/to/Hours>
% mkdir gems
% sudo gem install --install-dir gems --no-ri --no-rdoc gcal4ruby

2) Install MacRuby

http://macruby.org


